.TH rf 1

.SH NAME
rf \- A tiny and simple file finder

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B rf
[OPTIONS] PATTERNS...

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B rf
will find files based on glob patterns.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B "\-h, \-\-help"
.br
Show help message.

.TP
.B "\-V, \-\-version"
.br
Show version.

.TP
.B "\-b, \-\-basename"
.br
Only show the basename of results.

.TP
.B "\-b, \-\-dirname"
.br
Only show the dirname of results.

.TP
.B "\-v, \-\-invert"
.br
Invert matches.

.TP
.B "\-\-limit=[n]"
.br
Limit to [n] matches. The default is 0 which will return all matches.

